        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-cloud-cover:#ffffff;--color-sky-dust:#f6f6f6;--color-ocean-deep:#2c6bed;--color-night-sky:#1b1b1b;--color-deep-space:#404654;--color-subtle-mist:#a5cad5;--font-inter:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--color-cloud-cover);padding:48px 40px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:var(--font-inter);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;\"><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:row;gap:32px;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"flex:1 1 0;min-width:0;\"><h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:40px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;color:var(--color-night-sky);margin:0 0 24px 0;\">Share Without Insecurity</h2><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-night-sky);margin:0;\">State-of-the-art end-to-end encryption (powered by the open source Signal Protocol) keeps your conversations secure. We can't read your messages or listen to your calls, and no one else can either. Privacy isn't an optional mode — it's just the way that Signal works. Every message, every call, every time.</p></div></div><div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;border-radius:16px;background:var(--color-subtle-mist);min-height:200px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:24px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;border-radius:16px;background:var(--color-subtle-mist);\"></div><div style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:#2a7a80;border-radius:50px;padding:12px 22px;\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-inter);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;color:#ffffff;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">7a#v9^ht035v:q*</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"11\" width=\"18\" height=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg></div></div></div>",
